document_data.mainbody:
hantyni Evanara was a gold elf priestess of Labelas Enoreth from the elven realm of Siluvanede. She was a member of House Evanara.
She died and became an undying baelnorn. By 1370 DR, she had served her god for millennia at the Temple Beyond Time in Mhiilamniir in neighboring Eaerlann.
Alongside Susklahava Orbryn and Roanmara Neirdre, she was one of the Timespinners historians, oracles, sages, and seers whose advice was sought by the faithful on the temples occasional returns to the normal time-stream.
